Description: Bosch - Bruegel. Dulle Griet. The group of the adorning nudes in the background seems to be based on a similar group in background of Bosch' Last Judgment (Print, Kunsth. Mus. Vienna) [Ludwig von] Baldass, [Die Zeichnung im Schaffen des Hieronymus Bosch und der Frühholländer], Die Grafische Künste, N.F., III,1938, p. 79 [sic] [= N.F. II, 1937, pp. 18-26]. The reproduction here is rather small - look up Baldass, Bosch [= Hieronymus Bosch, Wien: Schroll] 1943, pl. [sic].
